## Backend & données

| Lib / service | Version | Rôle |
|---------------|---------|------|
| @nhost/nhost-js | `4.7.x` | Auth, GraphQL, Storage, Functions |
| graphql | `16.14.x` | Protocole |
| Hasura + Postgres | via Nhost Cloud | API + RLS (`nhost/migrations`, `nhost/metadata`) |
| @graphql-codegen/* | `6.x` / `5.x` | Codegen depuis `src/graphql/*.graphql` |

**Client GraphQL runtime** : constantes string dans `src/lib/graphql/operations.ts` + `graphqlRequest()` — **pas** d'import runtime depuis `src/generated/` (stub).

## Mobile & natif

| Lib | Version | Rôle |
|-----|---------|------|
| @capacitor/core + android | `8.4.1` | Shell Android (`androidScheme: https`) |
| @capacitor/app | `8.1.0` | Back button, deep links OAuth |
| @capacitor/browser | `8.0.3` | OAuth Google (Chrome Custom Tabs) |
